[quote=“NieX, post:2, topic:537854”]I’m eligible to do both client sided and server sided programming.

  1. Name: I’ll give it to you on Skype.

  2. Age: 17

  3. Skype name: Mexr46

  4. Position applying for: Server sided & client sided Programming.

  5. Experienced years in that position: Been developing since Allstar bases with silab client, so since the age of 11. (6 years). I feel more than confident to code to your desire with a 317 PI base.

  6. Time Zone: GMT + 0 (From England).

  7. Any other information i need to know? I speak two langauges fluently, Dutch and English. I’m able to host from home with an uptime of 99.5% for a temporary period (about a week) before upgrading to a VPS.
    I’m studying Java in education on a college course where I’m at and I’m doing the 2 year course in 1 year due to my sufficient knowledge of the language.
    Even though I’m only 17, I’m mentally as well as sounding and looking a lot older. (20’s).
    I can work up to 20 - 40 hours weekly on projects.[/quote]
